headline: Marketing Teams Achieved 342% ROI with Jasper, According to Total Economic Impact Study
summary: Jasper, the world's leading agentic marketing platform, today announced the results of a newly commissioned Total Economic Impact™ (TEI) study by Forrester Consulting. The study concluded that enterprises using Jasper realized a 342% return on investment (ROI) and benefits of $3.4 million over three years, with a payback period of less than six months.
